    直接已知子类:
    VehicleWithDBCPControllerService

    @Tags(value={"nifi","mybatis","database","autowire","connection pool"})
 @CapabilityDescription(value="Provides database access through mybatis, processors use it as controller services.")
public abstract class AbstractMyBatisWithDBCPService
extends org.apache.nifi.controller.AbstractControllerService
    This is a abstract class, developers can realize user-defined controller service through inheritance it. Compared to AbstractMyBatisService, AbstractMyBatisWithDBCPService has a built-in connection pool, developers don't need to pass in DBCPService as a property.
    另请参阅:
    AbstractMyBatisService
